---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="The Vessel - North Star Blog">

    <article class="blog-article">
        <header class="blog-header">
            <a href="/blog" class="blog-back">Back</a>
            <time class="blog-date">Mar 11, 2026</time>
            <h1 class="blog-title">First open AI &amp; Robotics Lab in Belgium</h1>
            <p class="blog-subtitle">The Vessel</p>
            <p class="blog-meta">Filip Nowak &middot; 4 min read</p>
        </header>

        <div class="blog-body">

            <div class="vessel-definition">
                <p class="vessel-word">vessel <span class="vessel-phonetic">/&#x02C8;ves.&#x0259;l/</span></p>
                <ol class="vessel-meanings">
                    <li><strong>A container.</strong> Something that holds things.</li>
                    <li><strong>A ship.</strong> A way to get somewhere.</li>
                    <li><strong>A carrier.</strong> Something that moves more than itself.</li>
                </ol>
            </div>

            <p>The Vessel is an open robotics and AI lab in the Antwerp port area, supported by Port of Antwerp-Bruges. It&rsquo;s the start of North Star&rsquo;s next chapter.</p>

            <p>Think of it as a &ldquo;forever hackathon&rdquo;: something that runs continuously, projects rotate, people come and go, but the knowledge compounds.</p>

            <figure class="blog-figure">
                <img src="/blogs/the-vessel/SCR-20260310-ozkx.jpeg" alt="The Vessel at Port of Antwerp-Bruges" loading="lazy" />
                <figcaption>The Vessel, Port of Antwerp-Bruges</figcaption>
            </figure>

            <p>In our first year we built the largest AI and robotics community in Belgium: 800+ builders, 18 events, 20+ hires through our ecosystem, active across six cities. The Vessel is the next step. Instead of one-off events, builders now get sustained access to hardware, industrial context, and real challenges.</p>

            <p>The Port of Antwerp-Bruges provides the space and operational context. For them, it&rsquo;s a new model for engaging emerging technical talent.</p>

            <figure class="blog-figure">
                <img src="/blogs/the-vessel/2026-03-10 16.58.10.jpg" alt="Inside the lab space" loading="lazy" />
                <figcaption>Inside the lab</figcaption>
            </figure>

            <p>During the founding period (through August 2026), we run two core programs. <strong>Open Lab Thursdays</strong> are weekly coworking days starting March 19th open to anyone who builds. <strong>Future in Bloom</strong> is a hackathon series where teams spend a day building around challenges in robotics, AI, and automation.</p>

            <figure class="blog-figure">
                <img src="/blogs/the-vessel/2026-03-10 16.56.25.jpg" alt="Open Lab session" loading="lazy" />
                <figcaption>An event at The Vessel</figcaption>
            </figure>

            <p class="vessel-closer">A vessel has a destination. This is the start of our journey.</p>

            <div class="vessel-cta-block">
                <a href="https://etoile.events/events/3ec37af2-d267-4031-bf8f-9cb69d89dbee" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="vessel-cta-link vessel-cta-primary">Join the first Open Lab Thursday</a>
                <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/north-star-agi" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="vessel-cta-link">Follow on LinkedIn</a>
                <a href="https://discord.gg/m5Hknymurb" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="vessel-cta-link">Join the Discord</a>
            </div>

            <p>We&rsquo;re open for partnerships. Whether you want to sponsor what we&rsquo;re building, bring a real AI or robotics challenge to the lab, or help shape the skills pipeline so the talent matches what you need, reach out: <a href="mailto:filip@ns2agi.com">filip@ns2agi.com</a></p>

            <p>Or fill out the below form:</p>

            <div class="vessel-tally-wrap">
                <iframe
                    data-tally-src="https://tally.so/embed/0QMBQ6?alignLeft=1&hideTitle=1&transparentBackground=1&dynamicHeight=1"
                    loading="lazy"
                    width="100%"
                    height="1200"
                    frameborder="0"
                    marginheight="0"
                    marginwidth="0"
                    title="Get in touch"
                ></iframe>
            </div>

            <script is:inline>
                var d=document,w="https://tally.so/widgets/embed.js",v=function(){"undefined"!=typeof Tally?Tally.loadEmbeds():d.querySelectorAll("iframe[data-tally-src]:not([src])").forEach(function(e){e.src=e.dataset.tallySrc})};if("undefined"!=typeof Tally)v();else if(d.querySelector('script[src="'+w+'"')==null){var s=d.createElement("script");s.src=w,s.onload=v,s.onerror=v,d.body.appendChild(s);}
            </script>

        </div>
    </article>

</Layout>

<style is:global>
    /* ── Blog article shell ── */
    .blog-article {
        max-width: 680px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 0 1.5rem;
    }

    .blog-header {
        padding: clamp(6rem, 12vh, 10rem) 0 clamp(3rem, 6vh, 5rem);
        border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
        margin-bottom: clamp(2.5rem, 5vh, 4rem);
    }

    .blog-back {
        display: inline-block;
        font-family: "Geist", sans-serif;
        font-size: 0.78rem;
        letter-spacing: 0.14em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: rgba(255,255,255,0.36);
        text-decoration: none;
        margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
        transition: color 200ms ease;
    }

    .blog-back:hover {
        color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
    }

    .blog-date {
        display: block;
        font-family: "Geist", sans-serif;
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        letter-spacing: 0.14em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .blog-title {
        margin: 0 0 1rem;
        font-family: "Instrument Serif", serif;
        font-style: italic;
        font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 5vw, 3.6rem);
        font-weight: 400;
        color: rgba(255,255,255,0.92);
        line-height: 1.08;
        letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    }

    .blog-subtitle {
        margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
        font-family: "Geist", -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
        font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.3vw, 1.15rem);
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: rgba(255,255,255,0.45);
        max-width: 48ch;
        font-weight: 400;
    }

    .blog-meta {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: "Geist", sans-serif;
        font-size: 0.78rem;
        letter-spacing: 0.06em;
        color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
    }

    .blog-body {
        padding-bottom: clamp(4rem, 8vh, 6rem);
    }

    .blog-body p {
        margin: 0 0 1.6rem;
        font-family: "Geist", -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
        font-size: clamp(0.95rem, 1.15vw, 1.08rem);
        line-height: 1.8;
        color: rgba(255,255,255,0.62);
        font-weight: 400;
    }

    .blog-body strong {
        color: rgba(255,255,255,0.88);
        font-weight: 700;
    }

    .blog-body h2 {
        margin: clamp(3rem, 6vh, 4.5rem) 0 1.5rem;
        font-family: "Instrument Serif", serif;
        font-style: italic;
        font-size: clamp(1.4rem, 2.8vw, 2rem);
        font-weight: 400;
        color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85);
        line-height: 1.15;
        padding-bottom: 0.75rem;
        border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    }

    .blog-body a {
        color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
        text-decoration: underline;
        text-underline-offset: 3px;
        text-decoration-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
        transition: color 200ms ease, text-decoration-color 200ms ease;
    }

    .blog-body a:hover {
        color: rgba(255,255,255,0.95);
        text-decoration-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
    }

    .blog-body blockquote {
        margin: clamp(2rem, 4vh, 3rem) 0;
        padding: 1.5rem 0 1.5rem 1.5rem;
        border-left: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
    }

    .blog-body blockquote,
    .blog-body blockquote p {
        font-family: "Instrument Serif", serif;
        font-style: italic;
        font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 1.6vw, 1.35rem);
        line-height: 1.5;
        color: rgba(255,255,255,0.72);
        margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    .blog-figure {
        margin: clamp(2rem, 4vh, 3rem) 0;
    }

    .blog-figure img {
        display: block;
        width: 100%;
        border-radius: 0.5rem;
        border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    }

    .blog-figure figcaption {
        margin-top: 0.6rem;
        font-family: "Geist", sans-serif;
        font-size: 0.72rem;
        letter-spacing: 0.06em;
        color: rgba(255,255,255,0.25);
        text-align: center;
        font-style: italic;
    }

    .blog-body a:focus-visible {
        outline: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
        outline-offset: 2px;
    }

    /* ── Vessel-specific ── */
    .vessel-definition {
        margin: 0 0 clamp(2.5rem, 5vh, 4rem);
        padding: 1.5rem 0 1.5rem 1.5rem;
        border-left: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
    }

    .vessel-word {
        margin: 0 0 0.8rem;
        font-family: "Instrument Serif", serif;
        font-style: italic;
        font-size: clamp(1.3rem, 2vw, 1.6rem);
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
        line-height: 1;
    }

    .vessel-phonetic {
        font-family: "Geist", sans-serif;
        font-style: normal;
        font-size: 0.82rem;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
        margin-left: 0.4rem;
    }

    .vessel-meanings {
        margin: 0;
        padding-left: 1.2rem;
        list-style: decimal;
    }

    .vessel-meanings li {
        font-family: "Geist", sans-serif;
        font-size: clamp(0.88rem, 1.05vw, 0.98rem);
        line-height: 1.7;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
        margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
    }

    .vessel-meanings li strong {
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.75);
        font-weight: 600;
    }

    .vessel-closer {
        font-family: "Instrument Serif", serif !important;
        font-style: italic;
        font-size: clamp(1.3rem, 2.5vw, 1.8rem) !important;
        color: rgba(255,255,255,0.82) !important;
        line-height: 1.3 !important;
        margin: clamp(2rem, 4vh, 3rem) 0 !important;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .vessel-cta-block {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 0.6rem;
        margin: clamp(2rem, 4vh, 3rem) 0;
        padding: 1.5rem 0;
        border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
        border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    }

    .vessel-cta-link {
        display: inline-block;
        font-family: "Geist", sans-serif;
        font-size: 0.88rem;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
        text-decoration: none !important;
        transition: color 200ms ease;
    }

    .vessel-cta-link:hover {
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9) !important;
    }

    .vessel-cta-primary {
        font-weight: 600;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
    }

    .vessel-tally-wrap {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin-top: 1rem;
    }

    .vessel-tally-wrap iframe {
        border: none;
        width: 100%;
    }
</style>
